flavorText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "209A9EC4400E9C3F7168D1AEF9C5F276", "It\'s past bedtime in the Baneswood Forest, but the watchman at the tower keeps vigil throughout the night. He offered up his lamp to light the lanterns along the paths, since they will keep the wild beasts away and guide any citizens to safety, as long as they remain lit. He warned me about some strange occurrences recently, so I should look out for anything out of the ordinary. In other words, anything that would raise concern for the residents of Hunter\'s Hill.")
calloutDescription: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "C46A1ECC4E74F0064746FA8D30F2D971", "A watchman shivers in the dark at his lonely post. He makes odd animal sounds perhaps to pass the time.")
name: CSQ_0033_TwilightDuty
